.TH APPFORM-SDK 3 "2026-05-03" "jhinno-appform-sdk" "Python SDK Manual"
.SH NAME
appform-sdk \- Python SDK for Appform 6.0-6.6 API
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B from appform_sdk import AppformClient, Config
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B jhinno-appform-sdk
provides a complete Python client library for the Appform 6.0-6.6 API,
including job submission, session management, file operations,
and organization administration.
.SH QUICK START
.PP
.RS
.nf
client = AppformClient(
    base_url="https://your-server.com",
    verify_ssl=False
)
client.auth.login(username="user", password="pass")
jobs = client.jobs.list_jobs()
.fi
.RE
.SH CONFIGURATION
.PP
