Access authentication APIs (AuthAPI)
.TP
.B client.jobs
Access job APIs (JobsAPI)
.TP
.B client.sessions
Access session APIs (SessionsAPI)
.TP
.B client.files
Access file APIs (FilesAPI)
.TP
.B client.apps
Access application APIs (AppsAPI)
.TP
.B client.organization
Access organization APIs (OrganizationAPI)
.TP
.B client.registry
