.TP
.BI client.jobs.batch_resume(job_ids)
Resume multiple jobs.
.TP
.BI client.jobs.batch_requeue(job_ids)
Requeue multiple jobs.
.TP
.BI client.jobs.delete_job(job_id)
Delete a job (6.6+).
.TP
.BI client.jobs.get_output(job_id)
Get job dynamic output.
.TP
.BI client.jobs.get_files(job_id)
Get job file list.
.TP
.BI client.jobs.get_history(job_id)
